Cookie Clicker is an addictive online game where the player must click on a cookie to accumulate points. The goal of the game is to collect as many cookies as possible by clicking on the main cookie and using the accumulated points to buy upgrades and bonuses that increase cookie production. The more the player clicks on the cookie, the more points they earn, and the more upgrades they can buy to boost cookie production. The game is simple but highly addictive, encouraging players to keep clicking to get more and more cookies.

Currently in beta, with more features coming soon!
